field.label:
<fieldset cf-questions="Please hit the start button below to get started">
<input type="radio" name="startProcess" value="start" cf-label="Start">
</fieldset>

<fieldset cf-questions="What type of evaluation is this?">
<label for="leadership">Employee/Leadership Evaluation <input type="radio" name="evaltype" id="leadership" value="leadership"> </label>
<label for="shortform">Short Form Evaluation <input type="radio" name="evaltype" id="shortform" value="shortform"> </label>
</fieldset>
<input type="number" cf-input-placeholder="" required="true" max="5" step=".01" name="employeeShortFormScore" id="employeeShortFormScore" cf-questions="What did the employee score on their review?">
<textarea name="additionalComments" id="additionalComments" rows="4" cf-questions="Please provide any additional comments about this performance review"></textarea>

<fieldset cf-questions="Would you like an Email of the form after everyone has signed off on it?">
<label for="yesEmail">Yes, I would like a copy Emailed <input type="radio" name="emailCopy" id="yesEmail" value="yesEmail"> </label>
<label for="noEmail">No, I don't need a copy Emailed <input type="radio" name="emailCopy" id="noEmail" value="noEmail"> </label>
</fieldset>

<input type="text" cf-input-placeholder="" required="true" name="signatureForForm" id="signatureForForm" cf-questions="By typing your signature in the box below, you acknowledge that all information provided has been filled out to the best of your knowledge.">

<fieldset cf-questions="Please hit Submit to Submit this Review to the Department Head">
<input type="radio" name="finalize" value="submit" cf-label="Submit">
</fieldset>
